   Inline-shim model: endbr(4) + shim(11: push rdi;push rsi;mov rcx->rdi;mov rdx->rsi;mov r8->rdx)
   + byte-identical SysV body + divergent epilogue (pop rsi; pop rdi before ret).
   Constant named K256W to avoid clashing with the already-defined K256 byte-list. *)

